{"id":298,"date":"2015-04-20T09:30:52","date_gmt":"2015-04-20T09:30:52","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.joannabarnden.co.uk\/?p=298"},"modified":"2026-05-17T07:42:20","modified_gmt":"2026-05-17T06:42:20","slug":"my-novel-is-here","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/my-novel-is-here\/","title":{"rendered":"My novel is here!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n\n\t<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/hb-arrives.jpg\" alt=\"hb-arrives\" width=\"198\" height=\"320\" \/>This will be a fairly short and possibly incomprehensible entry, for which I apologise, but I couldn&#8217;t let this moment pass without sharing it with the world. This morning the post lady knocked smartly on our door and delivered (unbeknownst to her) a package that I have been waiting for all my life.<\/p>\n<p>For there, inside a Panmacmillan envelope, was a gorgeous copy of the hardback of The Chosen Queen &#8211; my very own novel, published for real, under the pen name, Joanna Courtney, a name that I first spoke about writing under as a young girl.<\/p>\n<p>I am sitting at my desk now with the novel propped up before me and my heart feels as if it might (in time-honoured tradition) burst with the joy of it. It&#8217;s been a long, hard, often tearful slog to get to this point but I&#8217;d do it all again, three times over, to hold this &#8211; 395 pages of novel, wrapped up in a beautifully designed matt cover with shiny golden borders and my name on the front. I may cry. In fact, I&#8217;m surprised I haven&#8217;t cried already!<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/hb-arrives2.jpg\" alt=\"hb-arrives2\" width=\"218\" height=\"320\" \/>Enough. I must stop myself here or I will gush embarrassingly, so let me conclude with a huge thank you to everyone who&#8217;s helped me get this far (you&#8217;re listed in the book) and a simple message to those writers who who haven&#8217;t quite made it yet: If you&#8217;re still climbing the hill, keep going, cos it feels fabulous when you get there.<\/p>\n<p>Of course I still have to set foot on the huge path to actually selling copies, but I think for now, on this lovely day, I&#8217;ll just take a moment or two to enjoy the view from here.<\/p>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This will be a fairly short and possibly incomprehensible entry, <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":3051,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"slim_seo":{"title":"My novel is here! - Joanna Courtney","description":"This will be a fairly short and possibly incomprehensible entry,"},"footnotes":""},"categories":[23],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-298","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-blog"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/298","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=298"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/298\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4717,"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/298\/revisions\/4717"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3051"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=298"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/jc-static-copy.local\/wp-json\/